The Spanish bailout will include
conditionality that “may not only include that on individual
banks,” said  Thomas Wieser , head of the group that prepares
meetings for euro-area finance ministers.  Wieser, speaking to reporters in Vienna, didn’t elaborate.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
